{"type":null,"faqId":45453,"title":"如何将华为盒子与选购的蓝牙遥控器配对？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>靠近华为盒子（1米内）。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>请同时按住遥控器</span><span class=\"s2\">“OK</span><span>”和</span><span class=\"s2\">“音量+ </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165068\" style=\"width:0.2534722in;height:0.23888889in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”约8秒后松开。即可完成配对。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>等待一会，若遥控器能够使用，则配对成功。界面出现如图提示。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165069\" style=\"width:4.342361in;height:2.44375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165070\" style=\"width:4.342361in;height:2.44375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>配对成功后，下次可直接使用，无需再配对。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":246,"faqType":"遥控","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"973","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Remote","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCo